      <title>众议员吉姆·乔丹（俄亥俄州共和党）谈选举和参议院边境协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-15/rep-jim-jordan-r-oh-on-election-senate-border-deal-video</link>
