    <item>
      <title>中国央行在政策意外中维持关键利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/china-s-central-bank-holds-key-rate-steady-in-policy-surprise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行周一维持关键利率不变，同时仍向金融体系注入更多现金，这与将削减借贷成本以支持经济的预期背道而驰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/china-s-central-bank-holds-key-rate-steady-in-policy-surprise</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 01:23:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于中国人民银行维持利率不变，亚洲股市因美联储前景而上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/asia-set-for-mixed-start-after-taiwan-elections-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在交易员周五加大对美联储今年降息的押注后，亚洲股市大多走高。由于投资者对央行维持关键政策利率不变的决定不屑一顾，中国股市抹去了早前的跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/asia-set-for-mixed-start-after-taiwan-elections-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 22:06:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举结果被视为迫使妥协，台湾股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/taiwan-election-result-to-force-compromise-in-boost-for-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[执政的民进党在总统选举中获胜，但失去了立法多数，台湾基准股指上涨，引发了中国的温和反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/taiwan-election-result-to-force-compromise-in-boost-for-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 16:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
